race.comment: SATURDAY VIBES (4) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was classy enough to be competitive in this line-up. Has only missed a place once in four first-up attempts and a strong showing while fresh is on the cards. HARTSHORN (3) saves his best for this sprint journey and is racing in a purple patch of form at present. Cannot be discounted lightly. AMNESTY (2) has won over this course and distance and maps ideally from gate two. Expected to be in the finish. ROTH 'N' BUBBLE (6) loves this track and trip and will strip fitter second-up from the spell. In the mix. SPIRIT OF GIVING (7) next in line with winning rider Cormack in the saddle.
